view_recover_visible_formula
----------------------------

l1: $ nd _ctx (P u) $ by all_elim [#1]

view_recover_explicit_whole
---------------------------

l1: $ _wff $ by all_elim (t := $ u $) [#1]

view_recover_explicit_term_hole
-------------------------------

l1: $ nd _ctx (P _set) $ by all_elim (t := $ u $) [#1]

view_recover_visible_ctx
------------------------

l1: $ nd (join (hyp b) (hyp a)) (P u) $ by all_elim [#1]
